{"tid":118854,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死3隻]廈門地鐵站鑽挖地盤減壓艙起火釀3死","createTime":"2017-02-13T10:19:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-13T10:19:36.000Z","uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d0d91b28593f208e51d4590387f73478cb845e51","tid":118854,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T10:19:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170213/bkncn-20170213140345836-0213_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170213%2Fbkncn-20170213140345836-0213_05011_001.html&d=M59wMjr1KB2wSFKn0iQ%2Bgv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=3f5cb661\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170213/bkncn-20170213140345836-0213_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n福建廈門在建的地鐵2號線海滄大道站施工地盤的隧道鑽挖現場，昨晚約6時30分在減壓艙減壓過程中起火，導致3人燒傷，隨即被送院，但最終搶救無效不治。<br />\n<br />\n事發後，福建省委常委、市委書記裴金佳作出指示，要求做好事故善後處理工作，迅速查明原因，杜絕類似事故再次發生。市長莊稼漢要求全市範圍內全面開展事故隱患排查。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}